export default function Lessons() { return (

We will study the Book of Revelation in 17 (A-Q) parts.

(A) Some Keys to Studying the Book of Revelation

(A) Introduction [1:1-8]

(B) Christ and the 7 Golden Candlesticks [1:9-20]

(C) 7 Letters to 7 Churches [2-3]

(D) Vision of the Throne [4]

(E) Seven Seals [5-8:1]

(F) 7 Angels and 7 Trumpets [8:2-13; 9-11]

(G) A War in Heaven and a War on Earth [12]

(H) 2 Beasts and the Dragon [13]

(I) A Lamb Stood on Mount Sion [14:1-5]

(J) Judgement Hour Messages [14:6-20]

(K) 7 Last Plagues in Vials [15-16]

(L) Fall of Babylon [17-18]

(M) The Marriage and Marriage Feast of the Lamb [19]

(N) Millenial Kingdom [20:1-10]

(O) Last Judgment [20:11-15]

(P) All Things New [21-22:1-5]

(Q) Closing [22:6-21]

) }
